    "body": "close https://github.com/KMiri-rs/KMiri/issues/74\r\n\r\nNow kmiri shows accurate panic spot in the message:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/KMiri-rs/asterinas/blob/9e81921616402d2c30fff07b296419325a15eb2b/ostd/src/boot/smp.rs#L227\r\n\r\n```rust\r\nAn uncaught panic occurred: panicked at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/boot/smp.rs:227:5:\r\nassertion `left == right` failed\r\n  left: 0\r\n right: 1\r\nerror: abnormal termination: the program aborted execution\r\n  --> /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/osdk/deps/test-kernel/src/lib.rs:95:5\r\n   |\r\n95 |     core::intrinsics::abort();\r\n   |     ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ abnormal termination occurred here\r\n   |\r\n   = note: stack backtrace:\r\n           0: osdk_test_kernel::panic_handler\r\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/osdk/deps/test-kernel/src/lib.rs:95:5: 95:30\r\n           1: osdk_test_kernel::__ostd_panic_handler\r\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/osdk/deps/test-kernel/src/lib.rs:92:1: 92:30\r\n           2: panic\r\n               at src/main.rs:28:14: 28:40\r\n           3: ostd::boot::smp::construct_hw_cpu_id_mapping\r\n               at /home/zjp/.rustup/toolchains/nightly-2026-04-03-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu/lib/rustlib/src/rust/library/core/src/macros/mod.rs:51:21: 51:114\r\n           4: ostd::smp::init::{closure#0}\r\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/smp.rs:109:26: 109:73\r\n           5: spin::once::Once::<ostd::smp::IpiSender>::call_once::<{closure@ostd::smp::init::{closure#0}}>::{closure#0}\r\n               at /home/zjp/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/spin-0.9.8/src/once.rs:169:72: 169:75\r\n           6: spin::once::Once::<ostd::smp::IpiSender>::try_call_once_slow::<{closure@spin::once::Once<ostd::smp::IpiSender>::call_once<{closure@ostd::smp::init::{closure#0}}>::{closure#0}}, core::convert::Infallible>\r\n               at /home/zjp/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/spin-0.9.8/src/once.rs:255:29: 255:32\r\n           7: spin::once::Once::<ostd::smp::IpiSender>::try_call_once::<{closure@spin::once::Once<ostd::smp::IpiSender>::call_once<{closure@ostd::smp::init::{closure#0}}>::{closure#0}}, core::convert::Infallible>\r\n               at /home/zjp/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/spin-0.9.8/src/once.rs:212:13: 212:39\r\n           8: spin::once::Once::<ostd::smp::IpiSender>::call_once::<{closure@ostd::smp::init::{closure#0}}>\r\n               at /home/zjp/.cargo/registry/src/index.crates.io-1949cf8c6b5b557f/spin-0.9.8/src/once.rs:169:15: 169:77\r\n           9: ostd::smp::init\r\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/smp.rs:108:5: 111:7\r\n           10: ostd::init\r\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/lib.rs:158:5: 158:16\r\n           11: ostd::boot::start_kernel\r\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/boot/mod.rs:138:14: 138:27\r\n           12: ostd::arch::boot::miri_boot\r\n               at /home/zjp/KMiri/asterinas/ostd/src/arch/miri/boot/mod.rs:73:14: 73:28\r\n           13: miri_start\r\n               at src/main.rs:18:5: 18:34\r\n```",
